<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>HE ROLLS THE SEA AWAY</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Malai Pharo suok a tang te,
 Pathien in a pui dawk;
 A thil bawltheih dan suklatna'n,

[V2]
 Tuipi luong A chawlhsak.
 Tuipi luong A chawlhsak,
 Tuipi luong A chawlhsak;
 Isu tawh ka kinaih tieng gal lauh ding umlo,
 Tuipi luong A chawlhsak.

[V3]
 2. Gitloh na'n ka lung a chawk buoi,
 Setan thupiek ziekin;
 Mahleh Lalpa'n eithamuon hi,
 Tuipi luong A chawlhsak.

[V4]
 3. Ginlah, lauhna'n ei bawm mahleh,
 Isu tawh um khawm kau;
 A hehpihna'n ei ching intin,
 Tui luong chawlhsak in a.

[V5]
 4. Lal Isu, ka hun a tawp tieng,
 Na gam vakhawih mu'ng ka;
 Chun, Nang in ei pui in na tin,
 Tui luong chawlhsak in la.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>9</hymn_number>
</song>